ZH: 1. 他喜欢将贵重物品隐藏在保险柜里。
EN: He likes to hide valuable items in the safe.
ZH: 2. 她常常在衣柜里隐藏秘密的日记。
EN: She often hides her secret diary in the wardrobe.
ZH: 3. 他将身份证隐藏在护照夹里，以免丢失。
EN: He hides his ID card in the passport holder to prevent it from getting lost.
ZH: 4. 父亲在花园里隐藏了一些彩蛋，让孩子们去找。
EN: Father hid some Easter eggs in the garden for the children to find.
ZH: 5. 小狗常常把骨头隐藏在自己的窝里。
EN: The puppy often hides its bones in its own bed.
ZH: 6. 她需要在家中寻找她妈妈隐藏的礼物。
EN: She needs to search for the gift her mother hid at home.
ZH: 7. 这个坏人隐藏在树丛中，观察着他们的一举一动。
EN: The villain hid in the bushes, observing their every move.
ZH: 8. 孩子们喜欢在隐藏的地方玩捉迷藏游戏。
EN: Children enjoy playing hide-and-seek in hidden places.
ZH: 9. 她把真相隐藏在一个吓人的故事里。
EN: She hid the truth in a frightening story.
ZH: 10. 这幅画被隐藏在墙壁后面的画框里。
EN: The painting was hidden behind the frame on the wall.
ZH: 11. 他藏匿在这座城市的某个角落，避免被抓到。
EN: He hid in a corner of the city to avoid being caught.
ZH: 12. 商家常常在购物网站上隐藏一些特别优惠的商品。
EN: Merchants often hide special discounted items on shopping websites.
ZH: 13. 他把笔记本电脑藏在书架上，以保护隐私。
EN: He hides his laptop on the bookshelf to protect his privacy.
ZH: 14. 她把钥匙隐藏在一个安全的地方，以免遗失。
EN: She hides the keys in a safe place to prevent losing them.
ZH: 15. 这家餐厅隐藏在一个小巷子里，有点难找。
EN: The restaurant is hidden in a narrow alley, a bit difficult to find.
ZH: 16. 这位艺术家将他的身份隐藏了很长时间，直到他的成名。
EN: The artist hid his identity for a long time until he became famous.
ZH: 17. 他隐藏起来，等待合适的时机出击。
EN: He hides, waiting for the right moment to strike.
ZH: 18. 她把钱隐藏在一个旧袜子下面，以防家里发生偷窃。
EN: She hides her money under an old sock to prevent theft at home.
ZH: 19. 那个小偷将他的赃物隐藏在地下室里的箱子里。
EN: The thief hid his stolen goods in a box in the basement.
ZH: 20. 这座城市有很多隐藏的宝藏，等待探索者的发掘。
EN: This city has many hidden treasures, waiting for explorers to discover.
